Package de.uni_hildesheim.sse.qmApp

This package contains every class which is necessary to build the Qualimaster - Application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    This class controls all aspects of the application's execution.
    ApplicationActionBarAdvisor
    An action bar advisor is responsible for creating, adding, and disposing of the actions added to a workbench window.
    ApplicationWorkbenchAdvisor
    Class for configuring the workbench.
    ApplicationWorkbenchWindowAdvisor
    Public class for configuring the window of the Qualimaster-App.
    Perspective
    This class is responsible for providing the possibility to create several layouts.

Package de.uni_hildesheim.sse.qmApp Description

This package contains every class which is necessary to build the Qualimaster - Application. The package contains graphical layer as well as the business layer.
